<p>At the molecular level, GHK-Cu binds to specific receptors. This triggers a cascade of repair activities within <a href="/articles/best-peptides-for-skin-and-hair">skin and hair follicle cells</a>.</p>

<h3>Molecular Properties of GHK-Cu</h3>

<table class="tbl">
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Property</th><th>Value</th><th>Significance</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Molecular Weight</td><td>401.9 g/mol</td><td>Small enough for skin penetration</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Amino Acid Sequence</td><td>Gly-His-Lys</td><td>Copper-binding domain</td></tr>
