    <tr><td>Solubility</td><td>Water-soluble</td><td>Easy formulation in serums</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>Understanding these properties helps explain why topical application works. The small size allows penetration into deeper skin layers.</p>

<hr class="sep"/>

<h2>Skin Benefits: Beyond Surface Level</h2>

<p>Clinical studies demonstrate GHK-Cu's effectiveness for various skin concerns. Regular use can improve skin texture, firmness, and overall appearance.</p>

<p>Most users see noticeable changes within 6-8 weeks of consistent application. Improvements continue for several months with regular use.</p>

<h3>Key Skin Benefits Supported by Research</h3>

<table class="tbl">
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Benefit</th><th>Mechanism</th><th>Timeframe</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Improved firmness</td><td>Increased collagen I and III</td><td class="g">8-12 weeks</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Reduced wrinkles</td><td>Enhanced elastin synthesis</td><td class="g">8-12 weeks</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Brighter complexion</td><td>Antioxidant enzyme activation</td><td class="g">4-6 weeks</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Enhanced hydration</td><td>Glycosaminoglycan production</td><td class="g">4-6 weeks</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Faster wound healing</td><td>Stem cell activation</td><td class="g">2-4 weeks</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Reduced hyperpigmentation</td><td>Tyrosinase inhibition</td><td class="y">8-12 weeks</td></tr>
