<p>GHK-Cu is particularly beneficial for mature skin. It works well for sun-damaged skin and those with visible signs of aging.</p>

<p>It is an excellent option for people who cannot tolerate stronger treatments like retinoids. The anti-inflammatory properties make it suitable for sensitive skin types.</p>

<div class="d">
