    <tr><td>Strong acids (AHAs/BHAs)</td><td class="r">Avoid</td><td>Do not apply in the same session</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>Separate applications by at least 30 minutes if combining actives. Consider using GHK-Cu in the evening and other actives in the morning.</p>

<hr class="sep"/>

<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<div class="faq">

<details>
  <summary>How does GHK-Cu differ from regular copper supplements?</summary>
